Follow the instructions below to process EELS data in EMD format using the provided Python scripts.

Step 1: Download all files from this repository.

Step 2: Set up your Python environment using the TEM_env.yaml file.

Step 3: Run the Jupyter notebook (.ipynb) files sequentially to read the EMD file and extract the EELS spectra.

Step 4: Use Gatan DigitalMicrograph (GMS) to subtract the background from the final exported .msa EELS files for visualization and analysis.
